e of 1988 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/667"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–667","children":[],"tail":" effective one year after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-11-16"},"text":"Nov. 16, 1988","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/667/s136"},"text":"section 136 of Pub. L. 100–667","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1051"},"text":"section 1051 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id795b4603-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1982 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/247"},"text":"Pub. L. 97–247","children":[],"tail":" effective six months after "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1982-08-27"},"text":"Aug. 27, 1982","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/97/247/s17/c"},"text":"section 17(c) of Pub. L. 97–247","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t35/s294"},"text":"section 294 of Title 35","children":[],"tail":", Patents."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"id795b4604-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1975 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/596"},"text":"Pub. L. 93–596","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-01-02"},"text":"Jan. 2, 1975","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/93/596/s4"},"text":"section 4 of Pub. L. 93–596","children":[],"tail":", set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1111"},"text":"section 1111 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"miscellaneous","id":"id795b4605-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Repeal and Effect on Existing Rights","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Repeal of inconsistent provisions, effect of this chapter on pending proceedings and existing registrations and rights under prior acts, see notes set out under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1051"},"text":"section 1051 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"id795b4606-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"id795b4607-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For transfer of functions of other officers, employees, and agencies of Department of Commerce, with certain exceptions, to Secretary of Commerce, with power to delegate, see Reorg. Plan No. 5 of 1950, §§ 1, 2, eff. ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1950-05-24"},"text":"May 24, 1950","children":[],"tail":", 15 F.R. 3174, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/1263"},"text":"64 Stat. 1263","children":[],"tail":", set out in the Appendix to Title 5, Government Organization and Employees."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
